msg: Simplify the expected-output class hierarchy in the test suite by using
method overriding instead of implementing all behaviours in the base class
controlled by a set of flags.

shaped inheritance works predictably for the UnorderedRegexOutput class.
Raise a more informative exception in the unimplemented __cmp__ method.
Move all regex support to RegexOutput.
(RegexOutput): Override methods here to implement regex-specific
(UnorderedOutput): Move all regex support to UnorderedRegexOutput. Remove
the (unimplemented) __cmp__ method as it is already inherited.
